= Blog King = 

A collection of widgets and plugins for wordpress > 2.1.

The King Widgets are pretty advanced, since they are stuffed with options.

Details can be found here:

http://www.blog.mediaprojekte.de/wordpress-widgets-plugins/
  


P.S.
I started developing this code back in 2006. In the meantime i did more ruby development so some of the php code might not be too elegant. 




